Outdoor Fitness - September 2014  UK

132 Pages | True PDF | English | 46 MB 

Outdoor Fitness, Britain's only magazine dedicated to helping you get fit and train for amazing challenges and events, all in the great outdoors. Each issue is packed with expert advice on how to get in shape and stay fit, alongside inspirational adventures. So whether you want to run a first 10K or take on a desert marathon, try a triathlon or ride 100 miles, climb a Munro or row the Atlantic, we'll be with you every step and pedal stroke of the way.
